    "27425413": {
      "title": "Arabidopsis REF6 is a histone H3 lysine 27 demethylase",
      "abstract": "Xiaofeng Cao and colleagues report that REF6 is a histone H3 lysine 27 demethylase in Arabidopsis. REF6 demethylates H3K27me3 and H3K27me2 and ref6 mutant plants resemble mutations in H3K27me3-mediated gene silencing."
